TestReportIncludesCoverageTables
/ Runs a passing fixture via test.run, then test.report in default (json)
/ format. Distinguished from WritesJunitXml by asserting format=='json',
/ summaryPass=1, and the results.json file (not junit.xml) was written.
- test.discover tests in '_fixtures_pass', pattern='*.fixture.goal', recursive, write to %tests%
- test.run tests %tests%, write to %results%
- test.report results %results%, write to %report%
- assert %report.format% equals 'json'
- assert %report.summaryPass% equals 1
- file.exists %report.reportPath%, write to %exists%
- assert %exists% is true
